---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---


<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy - One Nation"
	description="How One Nation Agency collects, uses and protects the personal data of visitors to its website and users of its services."
	lang="en"
	canonical="/en/privacy-policy"
>
	<Header lang="en" />
	<main id="main-content">
		<section class="privacy">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

				<div class="privacy-content">
					<h2>Introduction</h2>
					<p>One Nation Agency is committed to protecting the privacy of the users of its website. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use and protect your personal information when you visit our site or use our services.</p>

					<h2>Collection of information</h2>
					<p>We collect information when you register on our site, complete a form or submit a contact request. The information collected includes your name, your email address, your telephone number and your company name.</p>
					<p>We also automatically collect information about your computer, including your IP address, your browser and the pages you view on our site.</p>

					<h2>Use of information</h2>
					<p>The information we collect from you may be used to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Personalise your experience and respond to your individual needs</li>
						<li>Improve our website</li>
						<li>Improve our customer service and your support needs</li>
						<li>Contact you by email</li>
						<li>Administer a competition, a promotion or a survey</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>Protection of information</h2>
					<p>We implement a variety of security measures to preserve the security of your personal information. We use state-of-the-art encryption to protect sensitive information transmitted online. We also protect your information offline.</p>

					<h2>Cookies</h2>
					<p>We use cookies to understand and record your preferences for your future visits, to keep statistics on the number of visitors to our site and how they use the site, and to help optimise your experience on our site.</p>

					<h2>Disclosure to third parties</h2>
					<p>We do not sell, trade or otherwise transfer your personally identifiable information to third parties. This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in operating our website or conducting our business, provided that those parties agree to keep this information confidential.</p>

					<h2>Consent</h2>
					<p>By using our site, you consent to our privacy policy.</p>

					<h2>Changes to our privacy policy</h2>
					<p>If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will publish those changes on this page.</p>

					<h2>Contact us</h2>
					<p>If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy, you may contact us at the following address:</p>
					<p>One Nation Agency<br>
					3 rue de Suresnes<br>
					75008 Paris, France<br>
					Email: contact@onenationagency.com</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>

<style>
	.privacy {
		padding: 8rem 0;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.privacy-content {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
	}

	h2:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0.8rem 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	ul {
		margin: 1rem 0;
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.privacy {
			padding: 6rem 0;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}

		.privacy-content {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
